        "path": "skills/settings/SKILL.md",
        "content": "---\nname: settings-manager\ndescription: |\n  Gerencia configuraĂ§Ăľes globais do Ravi. Use quando o usuĂĄrio quiser:\n  - Ver ou alterar configuraĂ§Ăľes do sistema\n  - Definir agent default\n  - Configurar DM scope padrĂŁo\n  - Ver todas as settings disponĂ­veis\n---\n\n# Settings Manager\n\nConfiguraĂ§Ăľes globais do sistema Ravi.\n\n## Comandos\n\n### Listar todas\n```bash\nravi settings list\nravi settings list --legacy\n```\n\n### Ver valor\n```bash\nravi settings get <key>\n```\n\n### Definir valor\n```bash\nravi settings set <key> <value>\n```\n\n### Remover\n```bash\nravi settings delete <key>\n```\n\n## Settings DisponĂ­veis\n\n| Key | DescriĂ§ĂŁo | Valores |\n|-----|-----------|---------|\n| `defaultAgent` | Agent padrĂŁo quando nenhuma rota casa | ID do agent |\n| `defaultDmScope` | Escopo padrĂŁo de DMs | main, per-peer, per-channel-peer, per-account-channel-peer |\n| `defaultTimezone` | Fuso horĂĄrio padrĂŁo | America/Sao_Paulo, etc |\n\n## â ď¸ Settings Depreciadas (use `ravi instances`)\n\nAs settings `account.*` foram migradas para a tabela `instances`. **NĂŁo use mais estas keys:**\n\n| Key depreciada | Substituta |\n|----------------|-----------|\n| `account.<name>.agent` | `ravi instances set <name> agent <agent>` |\n| `account.<name>.instanceId` | `ravi instances set <name> instanceId <id>` |\n| `account.<name>.dmPolicy` | `ravi instances set <name> dmPolicy <policy>` |\n| `account.<name>.groupPolicy` | `ravi instances set <name> groupPolicy <policy>` |\n\nA migraĂ§ĂŁo acontece automaticamente na primeira inicializaĂ§ĂŁo do daemon.\nPor default, `ravi settings list` esconde essas keys; use `--legacy` sĂł para inspecionar ou limpar restos antigos.\n\n## Exemplos\n\nDefinir agent default:\n```bash\nravi settings set defaultAgent main\n```\n\nConfigurar timezone:\n```bash\nravi settings set defaultTimezone America/Sao_Paulo\n```\n\nConfigurar policy por instĂ˘ncia (forma correta):\n```bash\nravi instances set main dmPolicy pairing\nravi instances set vendas groupPolicy allowlist\n```\n"
